> "We will be sending out a shuttle with a guard detail to replace
> you now.  How many of you will require evac.?"

A cough from Lord Elder and the sound of work is all that can be heard for a moment. "It will just be me." Lord Elder said finally. "The others, Kup and Grimlock, and some new Mech called Legacy all went to chase down the last of the Minions and a few Predacons." 

A grunt came from Lord Elder as a humming sound carried faintly over the communication link - the sound of power being restored. 

(TAG: Perseus)

A pause and then Lord Elder's voice came over the line again, "I am picking up low level subsurface seismic activity somewhere near to where Kup and Grimlock were suppose to be going. You picking this up?"

While leaving his line open to Perseus, Elder opened up another, "Kup, Grimlock, come in! What's going on over there?"

(TAG: Kup, Grimlock, Lord Perseus)

Preston
